I suggest obtaining the following:
    "Modern Cryptology"  by Gilles Brassard
    Lecture Notes in Computer Science
    Edited by G. Goose and J. Hartmanis
    #325, Springer-Verlag, NY

Very well written, talks about everything you need to know and lots of
references.

